=head1 NAME

	CL_RFC1123_6_1_3_1_Multi_req - Multiplex concurrent requests


=head1 VERIFICATION POINTS

	Verify that a NUT support multiplex concurrent requests

=begin html
	<UL>
	<DD><li>A name resolver SHOULD be able to multiplex concurrent<BR>
        <DD>requests if the host supports concurrent processes.
	</li>
	</ul> 

=end html

=head1 TARGET

	Client

=head1 SYNOPSIS

=begin html
<PRE>
	<A HREF="./CL_RFC1123_6_1_3_1_Multi_req.seq">CL_RFC1123_6_1_3_1_Multi_req.seq</A> [-tooloption ...]: KOI tool option
	See also <A HREF="../DNSConfig.pm">DNSConfig.pm</A>
</PRE>

=end html

